des:
GHome offers a complete smart home solution focused on freeing your hands. After activating Alexa skills, all GHome smart devices can be controlled by voice. 

The following is the operation guide:
(1) Download our "GHome" application on Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2) Register a new account (if you have already registered, please log in);
(3) Add devices in GHome App;
(4) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play, or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with the "Alexa" app. Search the Alexa Skills directory for "GHome". Click Enable skill of "GHome", then follow the steps to bind GHome App and Alexa； 
(5) Finally, you can use the Echo speaker to directly voice control the GHome App device.
